raw_icp_text:
Primary Persona: Tech-Forward CEO 
Company Size: 10-50 employees, $1-10M ARR 
Industry: AI/ML startups, SaaS companies, Tech services 
Pain Points: 
Manual sales processes consuming 40-60% of team time 
Inconsistent pipeline due to limited resources 
Difficulty scaling outbound without expanding headcount 
Need for 7x ROI improvement to compete with larger players 
Secondary Persona: Growth-Focused CTO 
Background: Technical leader juggling product development and revenue growth 
Challenges: 
Pressure to implement AI solutions that align with business outcomes 
Need to balance internal AI efficiency with customer-facing features 
Managing fragmented sales tech stack (average 10+ tools) 
Tertiary Persona: Overwhelmed Sales Manager 
Profile: Managing small sales teams (2-8 reps) with aggressive targets 
Key Issues: 
Lost deals due to delayed follow-ups (hours to days response time) 
Inability to personalize outreach at scale 
Lack of consistent lead scoring and prioritization
